Class Participant

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.sorter.Participant
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LapRaceParticipant, MarathonParticipant

    public abstract class Participant
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class Participant, can be instantiated as LapRaceParticipant or MarathonParticipant. Is created by reading data from input text files, and contains the information regarding one participant
    Author:
    team03
